channel.title: [Noname] Project
channel.description:
Well after joining [RL] about 10 minutes ago I was banned for Ban evasion due to the fact my other account was banned. Now I am going to have to start over on writing this thread.
My interest in Runescape and anything involving that subject has decreased rapidly recently. I am now focusing on other subjects that leave Runescape out of it. I have a Invision Power Board License along with 45-60$ to put into this project. Along with that I have decided that I am going to work on a general forum. This general forum will contain many categories of all sorts that will hopefully attract much traffic to the site. I decided that there will be no homepage or any other add-ons. It will just be a simple forum that will hopefully be a successful community. Anyone is free to join in on this Project and Ideas are appreciated.
Post below or contact: *
Note: There is not much information I can supply you with so early in the project, As it advances and more information is gathered I will be updating this post.
